      "comment": "CARISSA'S BABY (3) boasts a strong record this journey here with two wins and two minors from five tries. Placed last time (26.30) at Hobart in a Special conditions race, finishing second and beaten half a length. Looks suited and should go close. RICO BALBOA (1) was responsible for a modest effort most recently when seventh at Hobart over 340m behind Take His Cash (20.51) in a Restricted WIN. Has ability and can atone. RAVING LUNATIC (4) turned in a fair 4th placed finish last time at Hobart over 461m (26.02). Maiden this journey but has some solid runs behind him. Expected to feature in the finish. NEPTUNE FIREBALL (2) is worth including.",
